%% 图 1：DeFuzz 总体架构（出现在「四、技术路线 §1 总体架构」）
%% 渲染：mmdc -i architecture.mmd -o architecture.png -w 1600 -b transparent
flowchart TB
    CLI[DeFuzz CLI]
    Engine[Fuzz Engine 主循环]
    Prompt[PromptService<br/>基础提示词 + 编译器知识 + 机制契约]
    LLM[远端大模型]
    Compiler[Compiler<br/>插桩 GCC + gcov]
    Cov[Coverage Analyzer<br/>.gcda + CFG 导出]
    Oracle[MechanismOracle<br/>聚合多个不变量检查器]
    Inspector[BinaryInspector<br/>跨 ISA ELF 解析]
    Exec[Executor<br/>原生 / QEMU 用户态]
    Corpus[Seed Corpus<br/>持久化与家系信息]
    Flag[FlagScheduler<br/>正控 / 负控 profile]

    CLI --> Engine
    Engine --> Prompt --> LLM --> Engine
    Engine --> Compiler --> Cov --> Engine
    Engine --> Oracle --> Engine
    Oracle --> Inspector
    Oracle --> Exec
    Engine --> Corpus
    Engine --> Flag
    Flag -.极性.-> Oracle
    Flag -.编译选项.-> Compiler
